 "2004, approximately $2,903 of the valuation allowance related to benefits of excess tax deductions for stock", "bbox": [143.0, 855.2, 1092.9, 876.1]}, {"text": "options which will be credited to equity when realized.", "bbox": [143.0, 880.2, 601.2, 901.1]}, {"text": "10.", "bbox": [143.0, 942.5, 169.0, 963.3]}, {"text": "Employee Benefit Plan", "bbox": [189.9, 942.5, 392.6, 963.3]}, {"text": "The Company maintains a 401(k) savings plan covering substantially all of its employees. Eligible", "bbox": [184.7, 980.2, 1092.9, 1001.1]}, {"text": "employees may contribute up to 15 percent of their annual salary through payroll deductions, but not more than", "bbox": [143.0, 1005.2, 1092.8, 1026.1]}, {"text": "the statutory limits set by the Internal Revenue Service. The Company matches employee contributions at the", "bbox": [143.0, 1030.2, 1093.0, 1051.1]}, {"text": "discretion of the Board of Directors. During 2002, 2003 and 2004, the Company’s matching contributions totaled", "bbox": [143.0, 1055.2, 1092.7, 1076.1]}, {"text": "$0, $0 and $379, respectively.", "bbox": [143.0, 1080.2, 393.5, 1101.1]}, {"text": "F-25", "bbox": [598.3, 1463.6, 637.7, 1484.4]}]}